		"description": "<p><em>Wondrous item</em></p><p>This painted brass bottle weighs 1 pound. When you use an action to remove the stopper, a cloud of thick smoke flows out of the bottle. At the end of your turn, the smoke disappears with a flash of harmless fire, and an @Compendium[dnd5e.monsters.LTomFUTBrkRi0Pj5]{Efreeti} appears in an unoccupied space within 30 feet of you.</p><p>The first time the bottle is opened, the GM rolls to determine what happens from the @Compendium[dnd5e.tables.yZMFNfocj5qyVuOC]{Efreeti Bottle} table.</p>",
